        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "You have inherited the innate spellcasting ability of your ancestors. This ability allows you to cast "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Nondetection"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " on yourself at will, without needing a material component."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "You can also cast each of the following spells once with this ability: "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Blindness/Deafness"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Blur"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", and "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Disguise Self"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". You regain the ability to cast these spells when you finish a long rest. Intelligence is your spellcasting ability for these spells"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "html": "<div id=\"page-content\">\n<p>Source: Mordenkainen's Tome of Foes</p>\n<p><em>Prerequisite: Gnome (Deep Gnome)</em></p>\n<p>You have inherited the innate spellcasting ability of your ancestors. This ability allows you to cast Nondetection on yourself at will, without needing a material component.</p>\n<p>You can also cast each of the following spells once with this ability: Blindness/Deafness, Blur, and Disguise Self. You regain the ability to cast these spells when you finish a long rest. Intelligence is your spellcasting ability for these spells</p>\n</div>"
